主要翻译
 
revise [sth] ▦ vtr (text: edit, amend)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 校订, 修订  
 -- The proofreader revised the text.
 -- 校对员修订了文本。
 
revise [sth] vtr (update)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 修改 xiū gǎi TC Traditional Chinese 修改  (根据新信息进行)
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 更新 xiū gǎi，gēng xīn TC Traditional Chinese 更新 
 -- The HR team revised the staff guidelines.
 -- 人事团队修改了员工规则指南。
 
revise ▦ vi UK (study before an exam)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 复习 fù xí TC Traditional Chinese 複習  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 复习功课 
 -- Veronica has an exam on Tuesday, so she's revising.
 -- 维罗妮卡周二要考试，现在正在复习。
 
revise for [sth] vi + prep UK (study for an exam)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 为…复习 TC Traditional Chinese 為…復習  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 为…复习功课 
 -- Robert is revising for an exam.
 -- 罗伯特为一场考试复习功课。
 
revise [sth] ▦ vtr UK (review lessons)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 复习 fù xí TC Traditional Chinese 複習  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 温习 fù xí，wēn xí 
 -- I need to revise irregular verbs for the French test tomorrow.
 -- 明天有法语考试，我要复习一下不规则动词。
 
revise [sth] vtr (opinion: change)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 修改 xiū gǎi TC Traditional Chinese 修改  (观点等)
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 转变 xiū gǎi，zhuǎn biàn TC Traditional Chinese 轉變 
 -- Walter revised his opinion of the young man after listening to Mrs. Bradshaw singing his praises.
 -- 听了布拉德肖夫人的大力称赞，华尔特改变了对那位年轻人的看法。
 
revise [sth] vtr (numbers: adjust)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 修改, 修正  (估算等)
 -- Emma revised the figures according to the new forecast.
 -- 艾玛按照新的预测修改了数字。

在这些条目还发现' revise '：
在英文解释里：
bone up - brush up - come around - copy edit - cram - go back over - rethink - review - rework - rub up - study
中文：
修改 - 修订 - 订 - 校正

